2011-09-01T17:26:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-01/running-back-chris-johnson-agrees-to-four-year-deal-with-titans-espn-says.html
The  Tennessee Titans  and running
back  Chris Johnson  agreed to a four-year contract extension
worth a guaranteed $30 million, ESPN reported, citing a National
Football League official.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
